{
  "stem": "71.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tell you in a little while when we were on the train what happened when we-- we boarded the train, and we had an older man who was the-- the-- like the director of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in our compartment was a young soldier, and he was sitting on the bench, and one-- the first day he ask who went to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was like here high school or maybe a little higher education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a my-- a teacher of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was a physical education teacher, but she was a teacher, she has education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she says, I went to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He gave her a problem, an algebra problem, and she didn't know what-- how to do it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he asked again who-- I don't know if he wanted to find out if we come from a forest like we pretended that we are-- oh, we are really human beings that went to school one day or not.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he asked again if somebody else went and then a few people, they couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was standing there and I said, could I see that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to me, well, you didn't go to gymnasium, you're too young.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no, but can I just see it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I figured it out not the way he wanted, you know, but the way I felt that I-- and I figured it out and he looked at that and he says, you are right.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did you figure this out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I says, in my own way, I figured it out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was sitting on a bench.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, you come here, and you sit down on the bench.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't have to sit on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
